          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1698922561598-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped potatoes</strong> to a tray with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong>,<strong> </strong>season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 20-25 min or until the potatoes are crisp – these are your <strong>mini</strong> <strong>roast potatoes</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1698922565239-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1698922565239-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
